8
00:01:06.199 --> 00:01:10.503
<i>Mom reckoned she'd been</i>
<i>followed her whole life.</i>

9
00:01:10.505 --> 00:01:13.238
<i>Well. this one time.</i>
<i>we're at the beach.</i>

10
00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:17.442
<i>and Mom sees this guy</i>
<i>pointing a camera at us.</i>

11
00:01:17.444 --> 00:01:19.579
