<i>off at him.</i>

12
00:01:19.581 --> 00:01:23.816
<i>but he's just</i>
<i>frozen watching us.</i>

13
00:01:23.818 --> 00:01:29.021
<i>He says. "I'm sorry.</i>
<i>this is just the way it has to</i>
<i>be."</i>

14
00:01:29.023 --> 00:01:30.724
<i>And then he runs.</i>

15
00:01:31.659 --> 00:01:34.192
<i>Until slam!</i>

16
00:01:34.194 --> 00:01:36.294
<i>He jumps straight</i>
<i>in front of a car.</i>

17
00:01:36.296 --> 00:01:37.997
<i>Like it was</i>
<i>deliberate.</i>

18
00:01:37.999 --> 00:01:39.733
<i>Dead on impact.</i>

19
00:01:42.269 --> 00:01:44.971
<i>After the ambulance</i>
<i>takes him away.</i>

20
00:01:44.973 --> 00:01:47.907
<i>I pick up the</i>
<i>camera he dropped.</i>

21
00:01:47.909 --> 00:01:50.676
<i>It's a model</i>
<i>I've never seen.</i>

22
00:01:50.678 --> 00:01:54.179
