<i>of photos on it.</i>

23
00:01:54.181 --> 00:01:57.282
<i>and every</i>
<i>single photo</i>

24
00:01:57.284 --> 00:02:00.620
<i>is of Mom and</i>
<i>our family.</i>

25
00:02:00.622 --> 00:02:03.355
<i>At the swimming pool.</i>
<i>outside our house.</i>

26
00:02:03.357 --> 00:02:05.024
