132
00:07:08.529 --> 00:07:10.195
<i>Sorry. Yes?</i>

133
00:07:10.197 --> 00:07:12.731
I received a. uh...

134
00:07:12.733 --> 00:07:14.533
well. I guess you'd call
it an anonymous tip-off

135
00:07:14.535 --> 00:07:17.403
